b'Fulbright Outreach Lecturing Fund Now Seeking Hosts for Fall 2018'
b'U.S. Institutions are welcome to apply through OLF to bring current Fulbright Visiting Scholars to their institution for short-term lectureships of 2-6 days. To find a scholar, consult the Fulbright Scholar Directory. Please considering applying to bring these scholars to your institutions to lecture on their research or cultural topics.'
b'To listen to a recording of our most recent webinar, please visit our website.'
b'For more information and to find the application form, please visit our website: www.cies.org/olf, or contact Sarah Causer at OLF@iie.org'
b'www.cies.org/olf'
b'OLF@iie.org'
